OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,FHe carried out the procedures while
OL,7,Fworking at the trust's Southmead
OL,8,FHospital and also at the private Spire
OL,9,FHospital in the city.
OL,11,FToday (18 July), Mr Dixon was
OL,12,Fsuspended from practicing medicine for
OL,13,Fsix months after a tribunal ruled he
OL,14,Ffailed to provide adequate clinical
OL,15,Fcare.
OL,17,FMr Dixon maintains he always acted in
OL,18,Fgood faith and that complications can
OL,19,Farise from surgery. He has issued an
OL,20,Fapology to his patients.
