OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,FMs Hanman went to see Mr Dixon in 2017
OL,7,Fat the Spire hospital after
OL,8,Fexperiencing extreme stomach pains and
OL,9,Fwas told she needed mesh surgery.
OL,11,FShe said Mr Dixon didn't discuss any
OL,12,Fother options for potential treatment
OL,13,Fwith her and she was told she should
OL,14,Fundergo surgery as quickly as possible.
OL,16,F"He was adamant that the tear was
OL,17,Fthere and that I should have the
OL,18,Fsurgery," she said. "I took his advice
OL,19,Fas I thought he was a professional."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
