OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,FMs Hanman was later contacted by the
OL,7,FSpire hospital to say an investigation
OL,8,Fwas being carried out into Mr Dixon
OL,9,Ffollowing numerous complaints he had
OL,10,Fperformed procedures with appalling
OL,11,Fconsequences.
OL,13,FThe investigation revealed Ms Hanman's
OL,14,Fcare was substandard and that she had
OL,15,Fsuffered harm as a result.
OL,17,FMs Hanman said: "I felt violated. I
OL,18,Ffelt as though he'd personally gone
OL,19,Fout to harm me. I just felt cheated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
