OL,6,F"I can't see that I will ever be pain-
OL,7,Ffree," she said. "I just can't see
OL,8,Fthat that will ever happen. And that's
OL,9,Fsomething that sadly I've got to live
OL,10,Fwith and learn to cope with."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Spire Hospital
OL,13,Fdeclined to comment on individual
OL,14,Fcases.
OL,16,FA representative for Mr Dixon did not
OL,17,Frespond to requests for a comment on
OL,18,FMs Hanman's case.
