OL,6,FIn response to the Medical
OL,7,FPractitioners Tribunal findings
OL,8,Fagainst him, he said: "I have accepted
OL,9,Fthe findings of misconduct made
OL,10,Fagainst me by the Medical
OL,11,FPractitioners Tribunal.
OL,13,F"Despite my wrongdoing, my only wish
OL,14,Fwas to make (my patients) better. I
OL,15,Fconsidered that I was acting in my
OL,16,Fpatients' best interests, as the
OL,17,Ftribunal have accepted.
