OL,6,F"I am very sorry and deeply regret the
OL,7,Fmisconduct described by the Tribunal
OL,8,F.... I am committed to learning from
OL,9,Fmy mistakes and to .. regain(ing)
OL,10,Fpeople's trust and to continue working
OL,11,Ftowards becoming once again the
